profile:
We are family owned and operated since 1970 when Herman Marche set out to assist London residents and business owners with their sewer and drainage problems. In 1993, his son Barry took over the ownership and operations of the company, and today, we are London’s finest sewer, septic and drainage repair, replace and install company.

With over 15 employees, our professional team is friendly, highly trained in safety and certified in industry specific instruction. We are WSIB compliant and fully insured. Our fleet consists of the latest machinery including three service vehicles, two dump trucks, three excavators and a combination vac/power flushing sewer truck. With our sewer video inspections, our no dig- trenchless sewer line repair technology, and the latest tools and machinery, we can solve any drain and sewer problem you have. 

Wet basement, clogged drains? No problem! We handle foundation cracks, drain backups, and plugged and broken weeping tile.

Call us today to book your free Sewer Video Inspection!
